  "excerpt": "<h2><a href=\"/help/assistance-with-completing-the-application/\" title=\"Assistance with Completing the Application\">Assistance with Completing the Application</a></h2>",
  "content": "<div class=\"ds-l-row\" id=\"allowed-amount\">\n<div class=\"ds-l-md-col--12\">\n<h2><a href=\"/help/assistance-with-completing-the-application/\" title=\"Assistance with Completing the Application\">Assistance with Completing the Application</a></h2>\n\n<ul><li><a href=\"/help/whos-helping-me-complete-my-application/\" title=\"Who\u2019s helping me complete my application?\">Who\u2019s helping me complete my application?</a></li>\n</ul><hr><h2><a href=\"/help/special-circumstances/\" title=\"Special Circumstances\">Special Circumstances</a></h2>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"ds-l-row\" id=\"allowed-amount\">\n<div class=\"ds-l-md-col--12\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/help/immigration-status-questions/\" title=\"Immigration status questions\">Immigration status questions</a></li>\n</ul><hr><h2><a href=\"/help/getting-started/\" title=\"Getting Started\">Getting Started</a></h2>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"ds-l-row\" id=\"allowed-amount\">\n<div class=\"ds-l-md-col--12\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/help/what-health-coverage-do-i-have/\" title=\"Coverage questions\">Coverage questions</a></li>\n\t<li><a href=\"/help/ecn/\" title=\"How do I use my Exemption Certificate Number (ECN)?\">How do I use my Exemption Certificate Number (ECN)?</a></li>\n\t<li><a href=\"/help/why-am-i-being-asked-to-enter-my-preferred-spoken-and-written-language/\" title=\"Why am I being asked about language?\">Why am I being asked about language?</a></li>\n\t<li><strong>More articles on <a href=\"/help/getting-started/\" title=\"Getting Started\">Getting Started</a></strong></li>\n</ul></div>\n</div>\n\n<hr><h2><a href=\"/help/family-and-household/\" title=\"Family and Household\">Family and Household</a></h2>\n\n<ul><li><a href=\"/help/what-if-my-household-files-more-than-one-tax-return/\" title=\"What if I file more than one tax return?\">What if I file more than one tax return?</a></li>\n\t<li><a href=\"/help/what-do-i-need-to-enter-about-each-person/\" title=\"What do I need to enter about each person?\">What do I need to enter about each person?</a></li>\n\t<li><a href=\"/help/what-about-the-people-on-my-application-who-aren-t-applying-for-health-coverage/\" title=\"What about people who aren\u2019t applying for coverage?\">What about people who aren\u2019t applying for coverage?</a></li>\n\t<li><strong>More articles on <a href=\"/help/family-and-household/\" title=\"Family and Household\">Family and Household</a></strong></li>\n</ul><hr><h2><a href=\"/help/income/\" title=\"Income\">Income</a></h2>\n\n<ul><li><a href=\"/help/income-questions/\" title=\"Information about income you earned\">Information about income you earned</a></li>\n\t<li><a href=\"/help/income-questions-for-american-indians-and-alaska-natives/\" title=\"Income questions for American Indians &amp; Alaska Natives\">Income questions for American Indians &amp; Alaska Natives</a></li>\n\t<li><a href=\"/help/income-from-your-job/\" title=\"Income from your job\">Income from your job</a></li>\n\t<li><strong>More articles on <a href=\"/help/income/\" title=\"Income\">Income</a></strong></li>\n</ul><hr><h2><a href=\"/help/help-paying-for-coverage/\" title=\"Help Paying for Coverage\">Help Paying for Coverage</a></h2>\n\n<ul><li><a href=\"/help/whats-my-total-household-income/\" title=\"What\u2019s my total household income?\">What\u2019s my total household income?</a></li>\n\t<li><a href=\"/help/what-if-i-have-a-pre-existing-condition/\" title=\"What if I have a pre-existing condition?\">What if I have a pre-existing condition?</a></li>\n\t<li><a href=\"/help/what-help-is-available/\" title=\"What help is available?\">What help is available?</a></li>\n\t<li><strong>More articles on <a href=\"/help/help-paying-for-coverage/\" title=\"Help Paying for Coverage\">Help Paying for Coverage</a></strong></li>\n</ul><hr><h2><a href=\"/help/immigration-information/\" title=\"Immigration Information\">Immigration Information</a></h2>\n\n<ul><li><a href=\"/help/gain-immigration-status/\" title=\"Gain Immigration Status\">Gain Immigration Status</a></li>\n\t<li><a href=\"/help/citizenship-and-immigration-status-questions/\" title=\"Citizenship and immigration status questions\">Citizenship and immigration status questions</a></li>\n\t<li><a href=\"/help/immigration-status-questions/\" title=\"Immigration status questions\">Immigration status questions</a></li>\n\t<li><strong>More articles on <a href=\"/help/immigration-information/\" title=\"Immigration Information\">Immigration Information</a></strong></li>\n</ul><hr><h2><a href=\"/help/american-indian-and-alaska-native-questions/\" title=\"American Indian and Alaska Native Questions\">American Indian and Alaska Native Questions</a></h2>\n\n<ul><li><a href=\"/help/how-will-enrolling-in-coverage-through-the-marketplace-affect-me/\" title=\"How will enrolling in coverage affect me?\">How will enrolling in coverage affect me?</a></li>\n\t<li><a href=\"/help/how-do-i-know-if-my-tribe-is-federally-recognized/\" title=\"How do I know if my tribe is \u201cfederally recognized?\u201d\">How do I know if my tribe is \u201cfederally recognized?\u201d</a></li>\n\t<li><a href=\"/help/health-services-through-indian-programs/\" title=\"Health services through Indian programs\">Health services through Indian programs</a></li>\n</ul><hr><h2><a href=\"/help/eligibility-results-and-next-steps/\" title=\"Eligibility Results and Next Steps\">Eligibility Results and Next Steps</a></h2>\n\n<ul><li><a href=\"/help/should-i-have-my-information-sent-to-the-state-medicaid-agency/\" title=\"Should I have my information sent to the state Medicaid agency?\">Should I have my information sent to the state Medicaid agency?</a></li>\n\t<li><a href=\"/help/programs-savings-you-may-be-eligible-for/\" title=\"Programs &amp; savings you may be eligible for\">Programs &amp; savings you may be eligible for</a></li>\n\t<li><a href=\"/help/more-information-for-people-with-special-health-care-needs/\" title=\"More information for people with special health care needs\">More information for people with special health care needs</a></li>\n</ul><hr><h2><a href=\"/help/other-health-coverage-questions/\" title=\"Other Health Coverage Questions\">Other Health Coverage Questions</a></h2>\n\n<ul><li><a href=\"/help/what-if-my-coverage-ended/\" title=\"What if my coverage ended?\">What if my coverage ended?</a></li>\n\t<li><a href=\"/help/what-if-i-m-offered-a-state-employee-health-benefit-plan/\" title=\"What if I\u2019m offered a state employee health benefit plan?\">What if I\u2019m offered a state employee health benefit plan?</a></li>\n\t<li><a href=\"/help/what-if-i-have-coverage-through-an-employer/\" title=\"What if I have coverage through an employer?\">What if I have coverage through an employer?</a></li>\n\t<li><strong>More articles on <a href=\"/help/other-health-coverage-questions/\" title=\"Other Health Coverage Questions\">Other Health Coverage Questions</a></strong></li>\n</ul><hr><h2><a href=\"/help/privacy/\" title=\"Privacy\">Privacy</a></h2>\n\n<ul><li><a href=\"/help/prove-move/\" title=\"Submit documents to confirm your move\">Submit documents to confirm your move</a></li>\n\t<li><a href=\"/help/prove-marriage/\" title=\"Submit documents to confirm marriage\">Submit documents to confirm marriage</a></li>\n\t<li><a href=\"/help/prove-coverage-loss/\" title=\"Submit documents to confirm your loss of coverage\">Submit documents to confirm your loss of coverage</a></li>\n\t<li><strong>More articles on <a href=\"/help/privacy/\" title=\"Privacy\">Privacy</a></strong></li>\n</ul><hr><h2><a href=\"/help/change-in-circumstances/\" title=\"Change in Circumstances\">Change in Circumstances</a></h2>\n\n<ul><li><a href=\"/help/moving-to-a-new-state/\" title=\"What if you move out of state\">What if you move out of state</a></li>\n\t<li><a href=\"/help/change-in-circumstances-questions/\" title=\"Change in circumstances questions\">Change in circumstances questions</a></li>\n</ul>",
